qws - QuickWebShell

This project aims to become the default home page for all that users that loves QuickSilver (http://www.blacktree.com/) and are comfortable with a shell

Desiderata:
 - Super light startup (A class under YSlow)
 - Plugin structure to easily extend functionalities (even from remote files)
 - Some common shell functionalities (pipes, echo set)
 - Ability to store and lunch files
 - Cool interface (we hope :-)
 - Raking alghorithm like QuickSilver

Links:
http://orderedlist.com/articles/live-search-with-quicksilver-style